commit.title: [dune] [configure] Replace configure with minimal script for Dune.
commit.message:
[dune] [configure] Replace configure with minimal script for Dune.

The Dune build doesn't need most of the configure options, except for
`coqlib` which is indeed convenient, and some other meta-data.

We thus add a minimal configure script for it.

This is proof-of-concept, but eventually should be refined and merged.

cc: #7149
